The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation

 Arjun swipe

 Human resource development minister Arjun Singh has attacked Knowledge Commission chairman Sam Pitroda for opposing reservation in education.

 The chairman of the Knowledge Commission says he was unaware of the Constitution amendment (on reservation). If he is that ignorant, how can he be the chairman of the Knowledge Commission? Arjun asked a television channel.




